Plotted log2fold values (and the corresponding padj) are the output of the DESeq2 pipeline from a pairwise comparison between an NPC wt and an NPC ΔAC2C3 sample.
The standard DEseq2 analysis is run on the data from the Supplemental Table 9, which represents raw reads of the count-normalized cHiC replicates.

- "res.NPCwt_NPCdelAC2C3_10kb_bins_07_05_2025.tsv" file is the full DEseq2 output file from loop quantification at the Zfp608 TAD.
- "NPCwt_NPCdAC2C3_lolipop_input" file is the input file used to make the panelL graph. log2FC and padj values for this panel come from "res.NPCwt_NPCdelAC2C3_10kb_bins_07_05_2025.tsv" file for each loop. 
